5:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同老人家出去最好係跟團<br />\n上車，落車， 影相，  食野<br />\n愈多選擇愈麻煩<br />\n最慘係吃力不討好</blockquote><br />\n得出結論係下次跟團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87583fb76a746714ef31e03d8ef4ccdf2ce7da5b","tid":285522,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:29:01.000Z","msg":"比錢佢地兩個自己去算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa1cefa391093fd44e0664f2fd6853b795756636","tid":285522,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:31:11.000Z","msg":"而家你同兩老去旅行覺得好麻煩.<br />\n其實等於你細細個, 你呀媽呀爸帶你出街咁, 一樣覺得好麻煩.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3087ee2344cc1ad9f2a62816a694e97c098a97","tid":285522,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:34:34.000Z","msg":"獨遊先最好"},{"pid":"5c36ee9f496d1d8cf7ed09060b64902beeb76470","tid":285522,"uid":88134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:34:38.000Z","msg":"你細個果陣佢地帶你去旅行佢地都覺得好麻煩<br />\n呻完就算啦巴打"},{"pid":"70909bff76e4005c76f038ccc1f2f27588acb5cc","tid":285522,"uid":116896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:36:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家你同兩老去旅行覺得好麻煩.<br />\n其實等於你細細個, 你呀媽呀爸帶你出街咁, 一樣覺得好麻煩.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個唔識野唔識大體<br />\n但老人家就持老賣老, 唔尊重別人"},{"pid":"315e0c654e27853c315c8cf177d1397062ec34ef","tid":285522,"uid":43901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> agree,同佢地幾年一次已經夠,同佢地去過台灣同大阪,次次都激撚死我<br />\n永遠唔行得,12點出門口7點前已經要返屋企<br />\n用松屋部機都唔識用,有埋中文字都話自己唔識<br />\n唔識同當地人講又要嘈加把口<br />\n去景點一句&quot;唔想睇,你自己睇喇&quot;就走左去<br />\n食野係咁批評,食咩都話冇特別唔好食之後黑面</blockquote><br />\n又嗌貴又嗌唔好食<br />\n又話人地搵佢笨<br />\n之後開始話「都係香港好」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我老豆都係咁 任何野要俾錢就話人搵佢苯 博物館要俾錢都係搵苯<br />\n但佢更差既係去歐洲樣樣都話 「大陸都有啦 仲勁過呢d喎」<br />\n唉我屌 都係等佢自己死上大陸旅行好過 去乜柒歐洲</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樣樣都可以比，野食，建築，交通，總之你推介就踩一踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解可以全中 一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次我問佢可唔可以唔好樣樣野都彈 佢就罵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87c038b3965c6f90dac187bd05fac483557b9c3","tid":285522,"uid":71571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:50:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你細個果陣佢地帶你去旅行佢地都覺得好麻煩<br />\n呻完就算啦巴打</blockquote><br />\n純粹呻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088888f4fac5ede1bd59d758c6b55145f8363d11","tid":285522,"uid":71571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:51:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比錢佢地兩個自己去算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地想一家人開開心心去啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f16ef9e33f542a443f1006f8db2f524c49c76a","tid":285522,"uid":71571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:51:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家你同兩老去旅行覺得好麻煩.<br />\n其實等於你細細個, 你呀媽呀爸帶你出街咁, 一樣覺得好麻煩.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個唔識野唔識大體<br />\n但老人家就持老賣老, 唔尊重別人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca7945780c57d1de06b51e7ce657ffe68ba4fd3b","tid":285522,"uid":71571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:53:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/n