/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過煩在要不停幫佢影，影完又話呢到唔好要再影，同埋佢買野好慢，揀好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5afbff3a6a2afc6f781dfcb1a068e0b7c3dc0217","tid":285522,"uid":52188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:28:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好彩從來都唔會同佢地去<br />\n一定估到唔岩玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係佢地一把年紀都想陪佢地去下既</blockquote><br />\n睇情況啦，有時兩老可能唔需要你陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d9b4eb0cce98c608529f60fac91e4005576e2c","tid":285522,"uid":96300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:31:03.000Z","msg":"同另一半個兩老去 去完發誓呢次係第一次 亦都會係最後一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返到屋企突然覺得自己個兩老真係好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa4727261489a66699c0c48d399860776967975","tid":285522,"uid":86051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:40:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家你同兩老去旅行覺得好麻煩.<br />\n其實等於你細細個, 你呀媽呀爸帶你出街咁, 一樣覺得好麻煩.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個唔識野唔識大體<br />\n但老人家就持老賣老, 唔尊重別人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你都on9<br />\n細個唔識野點撚同老人家呀<br />\n就算任性老豆老母冇責任？<br />\n但咁大個人都唔識體諒下個仔？<br />\n兩件事根本唔撚同<br />\n埋怨對件事根本冇幫助"},{"pid":"6ca178f521cd4e09717a33383ddf29487fdcdd1a","tid":285522,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:45:23.000Z","msg":"唔覺 次次同佢地都係食好住好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一餐飯可以食過萬銀 住溫泉旅館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}